OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening, some of the showers may be
OL,8,Fheavy at times. Drier conditions to
OL,9,Ffollow overnight with showers
OL,10,Fgradually fading. A chilly night with
OL,11,Fbelow average temperatures, a few
OL,12,Fdegrees cooler in rural parts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA dry start to Wednesday
OL,15,Fwith hazy sunshine in the morning.
OL,16,FShowers developing from late morning,
OL,17,Fthese may be heavy and turn thundery
OL,18,Fby the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
